INSERT INTO `post` (`id`, `authorId`, `parentId`, `title`, `metaTitle`, `slug`, `summary`, `published`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`, `publishedAt`, `content`) VALUES
(1, 1, NULL, 'VQMod(script)', NULL, 'VQModscript', '', 1, '2020-10-22 03:52:35', '2020-11-02 11:59:15', NULL, 'VQmod adalah script virtual yang digunakan untuk menambah atau mengubah script core yang ada dalam opencart, tujuannya supaya dalam pengembangan extension programer tidak perlu mengubah script core opencart. hal ini penting supaya script core tidak ada modifikasi didalamnya.\r\n[br/]\r\ncontoh sederhana script VQmod(xml)\r\n\r\n[pre]\r\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n	&lt;modification\r\n		xmlns=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod\"\r\n		xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\r\n		xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vqmod/vqmod/master/vqmod.xsd\"\r\n	>\r\n	&lt;id>Replace 123 with ABC&lt;/id>\r\n	&lt;version>1.0.0&lt;/version>\r\n	&lt;vqmver>2.5.0&lt;/vqmver>\r\n	&lt;author>qphoria&lt;/author>\r\n\r\n		&lt;file name=\"relative/path/myfile.php\">\r\n			&lt;operation>\r\n				&lt;search position=\"replace\">&lt;![CDATA[\r\n				$var = \'123\';\r\n				]]>&lt;/search>\r\n\r\n				&lt;add>&lt;![CDATA[\r\n				$var = \'ABC\';\r\n				]]>&lt;/add>\r\n			&lt;/operation>\r\n		&lt;/file>\r\n	&lt;/modification>\r\n[/pre]\r\n&lt;!-- update 23/10/2020 -->[br/]\r\nSkrip ini hanya mengubah nilai variabel \"myfile.php\" dari \"123\" menjadi \"ABC\" sebelum disertakan.[br/]\r\n[em-merah]This script simply changes the value of a variable of \"myfile.php\" from \"123\" to \"ABC\" before it gets included.[/em][br/]\r\n##Syntax[br/]\r\nvQmod mendukung sejumlah parameter:[br/]\r\n[em-merah]vQmod supports a number of parameters:[/em][br/]\r\n[em]Modification[/em]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]Ini adalah tingkat file tertinggi dan hanya boleh ada satu\r\n	[br/][em-merah]This is the highest level of the file and there can only be one[/em][/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[em]modification / id[/em]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]Ini adalah nama dan deskripsi mod tersebut.\r\n	[br/][em-merah]This is the name and description of the mod.[/em][/li]\r\n	[li]Format: Teks bentuk bebas. (Informasi).\r\n	[br/][em-merah]Format: Free form text. (Informational).[/em][/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[em]modification / version[/em]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]Ini adalah versi mod.\r\n	[br/][em-merah]This is the version of the mod.[/em][/li]\r\n	[li]Format: Angka dan Desimal (1.0.0) (Informasi)\r\n	[br/][em-merah]Format: Number and Decimal (1.0.0) (Informational)[/em][/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[em]modification / version[/em]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]Ini adalah versi mod.\r\n	[br/][em-merah]This is the version of the mod.[/em][/li]\r\n	[li]Format: Angka dan Desimal (1.0.0) (Informasi)\r\n	[br/][em-merah]Format: Number and Decimal (1.0.0) (Informational)[/em][/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n&lt;!-- 26/10/2020 -->[br/]\r\n[em]modification / vqmver[/em]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]Ini adalah versi VirtualQMod minimum yang diperlukan agar skrip dapat berfungsi[br/][em-merah]This is the minimum required version of VirtualQMod needed for the script to work.[/em][/li]\r\n	[li]Format: Angka dan Desimal (1.0.0) (Informasi)[br/][em-merah]Format: Number and Decimal (1.0.0) (Informational)[/em][/li]\r\n	[li]Atribut required = \"true\" dapat secara opsional disetel untuk menonaktifkan skrip jika tidak memenuhi versi yang diperlukan (Ditambahkan dari 2.4.0)[br/][em-merah]A required=\"true\" attribute can be optionally set to disable the script if it doesn\'t meet the required version (Added from 2.4.0)[/em][/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[em]modification / author[/em]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]Ini adalah pembuat mod[br/][em-merah]This is the author of the mod.[/em][/li]\r\n	[li]Format: Teks bentuk bebas (Informasi)[br/][em-merah]Format: Free form text (Informational)[/em][/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[em]modification / file[/em]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]Ini adalah nama file yang akan diubah[br/][em-merah]This is the name of the file to modify[/em][/li]\r\n	[li]Membutuhkan atribut \"name\" sebagai nama file relatif ke lokasi file index.php utama (misalnya catalog / controller / product / product.php). Dapat dipisahkan dengan koma untuk diterapkan ke beberapa file sekaligus (2.3.0 +) Atribut nama mendukung karakter wildcard (*) untuk pembuatan jalur dinamis. Setiap karakter pengganti dibatasi pada satu tingkat direktori[br/][em-merah]Requires attribute \"name\" as relative filename to the location of the main index.php file (e.g. catalog/controller/product/product.php). Can be delimited with commas to apply to multiple files at once (2.3.0 +) Name attribute supports a wildcard (*) character for dynamic path building. Each wildcard is limited to a single directory level.[/em][/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n	[pre]\r\n	- catalog/view/theme/*/template/product/product.tpl\r\n	- catalog/view/theme/*/*/product/product.tpl\r\n	- etc\r\n	[/pre]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]Mungkin ada beberapa tag file dalam satu file xml. Setiap file dapat memiliki rangkaian operasinya sendiri[br/][em-merah]There can be multiple file tags in a single xml file. Each file can have its own set of operations[/em][/li]\r\n	[li]Atribut opsional \"jalur\" dapat digunakan sebagai awalan nama file untuk menghindari pengulangan. Ini hanya ditambahkan ke nama file dan [strong]tidak[/strong] ada validasi yang dicoba (2.3.0 +)[br/][em-merah]Optional attribute \"path\" can be used to prefix file name\'s to avoid repetition. This is simply prepended to the file names and [strong]no[/strong] validation is attempted (2.3.0 +)[/em][/li]\r\n	[li]Atribut opsional \"error\" disetel ke log | lewati | batalkan[br/][em-merah]Optional attribute \"error\" set to log|skip|abort[/em][/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li][strong] lewati [/strong] berarti itu hanya akan mengabaikan file ini[br/][em-merah][strong]skip[/strong] means it will simply ignore this file.[/em][/li]\r\n		[li][strong] log [/strong] sama dengan lewati, tetapi mencatat kesalahan. [strong] (default) [/strong][br/][em-merah][strong]log[/strong] is the same as skip, but logs the error. [strong](default)[/strong][/em][/li]\r\n		[li][strong] abort [/strong] berarti mencatat kesalahan dan membatalkan operasi yang tersisa dalam skrip xml tersebut. Itu tidak mengembalikan perubahan ke file lain yang sudah dibuat dalam skrip itu dan tidak menghentikan file xml lainnya[br/][em-merah][strong]abort[/strong] means to log the error and cancel the remaining operations in that particular xml script. It does not revert changes to other files already made in that script and doesn\'t stop other xml files.[/em][/li]\r\n		[li][strong]Wildcard jalur akan mengabaikan \"kesalahan\" atribut-benar[/strong][br/][em-merah][strong]Wildcard paths will ignore the \"error\" attribute completely[/strong][/em][/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[em]modification / file / operation[/em]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]This is the wrapper of the actual operation occurring.[/li]\r\n	[li]There can be multiple operations to the same [em]file[/em] tag.[/li]\r\n	[li]Optional attribute \"info\" suggested. May be used by vQmod/vQmod Manager for OC in the future but at present isn\'t used. This is however ideal for making files easier to read[/li]\r\n	[li]Optional attribute \"error\" set to skip|log|abort[/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li][em]skip[/em] means all other operations will be applied even if one cannot. There will be no error in the log.[/li]\r\n		[li][em]log[/em] is the same as skip, but logs the error.[/li]\r\n		[li][em]abort[/em] means to log the error and revert to the original source. [em](default)[/em][/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[em]modification / file / operation / ignoreif[/em]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]This allows for a search to be made on a file. This search works across [em]multiple lines[/em] not just single lines. This tag is optional and if the search is found, the operation is skipped[/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li]Optional attribute \"regex\' set to true|false. Format of data inside tag then requires delimiters for regex as it uses the standard preg_match method for php. This attribute defaults to false[/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[em]modification / file / operation / search[/em]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]This is the first required step of the operation.[/li]\r\n	[li]&lt;strong>Can only search single lines&lt;/strong>, both fully and partially. But [em]offset[/em] and [em]index[/em] attributes will assist.[/li]\r\n	[li]Automatically trims whitespace and linebreaks[/li]\r\n	[li]One &lt;search&gt; tag per &lt;operation&gt; tag[/li]\r\n	[li]Use CDATA tags to wrap code.[/li]\r\n	[li]Required attribute \"position\" set to before|after|replace|top|bottom||ibefore|iafter.[/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li][em]replace[/em] will replace the data in the [em]search[/em] tag with the data in the [em]add[/em] tag. (default)[/li]\r\n		[li][em]before[/em] will insert the [em]add[/em] data before the [em]search[/em] data[/li]\r\n		[li][em]after[/em] will insert the [em]add[/em] data after the [em]search[/em] data[/li]\r\n		[li][em]top[/em] will insert the [em]add[/em] data at the top of the file. The [em]search[/em] data is ignored.[/li]\r\n		[li][em]bottom[/em] will insert the [em]add[/em] data at the bottom of the file. The [em]search[/em] data is ignored.[/li]\r\n		[li][em]all[/em] Deprecated as of 2.4.0[/li]\r\n		[li][em]ibefore[/em] will insert the code before the search inline instead of the line before[/li]\r\n		[li][em]iafter[/em] will insert the code afterthe search inline instead of the line before[/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n	[li]Optional attribute \"offset\" to work with the position[/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li]if the search position is before and offset 3 it will put the [em]add[/em] data before the line, 3 lines above the searched line[/li]\r\n		[li]if the search position is after and offset 3 it will put the [em]add[/em] data after the line, 3 lines below the searched line[/li]\r\n		[li]if the search position is replace and offset 3 it will remove the code from the search line and the next 3 lines and replace it with the [em]add[/em] data[/li]\r\n		[li]if the search position is top and offset 3 it will put the code before the line, 3 lines below the top of the file[/li]\r\n		[li]if the search position is bottom and offset 3 it will put the code after the line, 3 lines above the bottom of the file[/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n	[li]Optional attribute \"index\" for specifying which instances of a search tag should be acted on[/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li]If the search string is \"echo\" and there are 5 echos in the file, but only want to replace the 1st and 3rd, use index=\"1,3\"[/li]\r\n		[li]Comma delimited for multiple instances starting with \"1\"[/li]\r\n		[li]Leave out or set to FALSE to replace all instances. (default)[/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n	[li]Optional attribute \"regex\" for specifying whether or not to search a regex pattern.[/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li]If true, the [em]search[/em] data should be a valid regex pattern[/li]\r\n		[li]Leave out or set to FALSE to use normal string search (default)[/li]\r\n		[li]Does not apply to ibefore and iafter[/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n	[li]Optional attribute \"trim\" set to true|false[/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li]true will trim away whitespace and linebreaks.[/li]\r\n		[li]leave out or set to true to trim. (default is true)[/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[em]modification / file / operation / add[/em]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]This is the second required step of the operation.[/li]\r\n	[li]Can be [em]multiple[/em] lines[/li]\r\n	[li]One &lt;add&gt; tag per &lt;operation&gt; tag.[/li]\r\n	[li]Location of added data depends on the position attribute of the [em]search[/em] command.[/li]\r\n	[li]Use CDATA tags to wrap code.[/li]\r\n	[li]&lt;strong>[em]NEW IN 2.6.0[/em]&lt;/strong>: &lt;add&gt; tag now supports all the search attributes.[/li]\r\n	[li]&lt;strong>[em]Attributes in the [/em]&lt;/strong>&lt;strong>[em]&lt;add&gt;[/em]&lt;/strong>&lt;strong>[em] tag will override attributes in the [/em]&lt;/strong>&lt;strong>[em]&lt;search&gt;[/em]&lt;/strong>&lt;strong>[em] tag.[/em]&lt;/strong>[/li]\r\n	[li]Optional attribute \"position\" set to before|after|replace|top|bottom|ibefore|iafter.[/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li][em]replace[/em] will replace the data in the [em]search[/em] tag with the data in the [em]add[/em] tag. (default)[/li]\r\n		[li][em]before[/em] will insert the [em]add[/em] data before the [em]search[/em] data[/li]\r\n		[li][em]after[/em] will insert the [em]add[/em] data after the [em]search[/em] data[/li]\r\n		[li][em]top[/em] will insert the [em]add[/em] data at the top of the file. The [em]search[/em] data is ignored.[/li]\r\n		[li][em]bottom[/em] will insert the [em]add[/em] data at the bottom of the file. The [em]search[/em] data is ignored.[/li]\r\n		[li][em]ibefore[/em] will insert the code before the search inline instead of the line before[/li]\r\n		[li][em]iafter[/em] will insert the code afterthe search inline instead of the line before[/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n	[li]Optional attribute \"offset\" to work with the position[/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li]if the search position is before and offset 3 it will put the [em]add[/em] data before the line, 3 lines above the searched line[/li]\r\n		[li]if the search position is after and offset 3 it will put the [em]add[/em] data after the line, 3 lines below the searched line[/li]\r\n		[li]if the search position is replace and offset 3 it will remove the code from the search line and the next 3 lines and replace it with the [em]add[/em] data[/li]\r\n		[li]if the search position is top and offset 3 it will put the code before the line, 3 lines below the top of the file[/li]\r\n		[li]if the search position is bottom and offset 3 it will put the code after the line, 3 lines above the bottom of the file[/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n	[li]Optional attribute \"index\" for specifying which instances of a search tag should be acted on[/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li]If the search string is \"echo\" and there are 5 echos in the file, but only want to replace the 1st and 3rd, use index=\"1,3\"[/li]\r\n		[li]Comma delimited for multiple instances starting with \"1\"[/li]\r\n		[li]Leave out or set to FALSE to replace all instances. (default)[/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n	[li]Optional attribute \"regex\" for specifying whether or not to search a regex pattern.[/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li]If true, the [em]search[/em] data should be a valid regex pattern[/li]\r\n		[li]Leave out or set to FALSE to use normal string search (default)[/li]\r\n		[li]Does not apply to ibefore and iafter[/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n	[li]Optional attribute \"trim\" set to true|false[/li]\r\n	[ul]\r\n		[li]true will trim away whitespace and linebreaks.[/li]\r\n		[li]leave out or set to true to trim. (default is true)[/li]\r\n	[/ul]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[em]&lt;![CDATA[ ]]>[/em]\r\n[ul]\r\n	[li]These are called CDATA tags and they are used by xml to specify that the data between should not be evaluated. It\'s recommended you always use these for data between the and operation tags[/li]\r\n[/ul]'),
(2, 1, NULL, 'VQMod(example)', NULL, 'VQModexample', '', 1, '2020-10-27 03:35:11', '2020-11-03 12:00:05', NULL, '#Examples of use\r\n##\"Replace\" Example\r\n[ol]\r\n	[li]Create a new text file and call it \"replace-demo.xml\"[/li]\r\n	[li]Add the minimum required xml structure[/li]\r\n[/ol]\r\n\r\nInput\r\n[pre]\r\n	$var = \'ABC\';\r\n[/pre]\r\nScript\r\n[pre]\r\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n&lt;modification\r\n                xmlns=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod\"\r\n                xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\r\n                xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vqmod/vqmod/master/vqmod.xsd\">\r\n                >\r\n	&lt;id>Replace ABC with 123&lt;/id>\r\n	&lt;version>1.0&lt;/version>\r\n	&lt;vqmver>2.X&lt;/vqmver>\r\n	&lt;author>xxx&lt;/author>\r\n	&lt;file name=\"path/to/myfile.php\">\r\n	&lt;operation info=\"replace ABC with 123\">\r\n		&lt;search position=\"replace\">&lt;![CDATA[\r\n		$var = \'ABC\';\r\n		]]>&lt;/search>\r\n		&lt;add>&lt;![CDATA[\r\n		$var = \'123\';\r\n		]]>&lt;/add>\r\n	&lt;/operation>\r\n	&lt;/file>\r\n&lt;/modification>\r\n[/pre]\r\nOutput\r\n[pre]\r\n$var = \'123\';\r\n[/pre]\r\n##\"Before\" Example\r\n\r\n[ol]\r\n[li]Create a new text file and call it \"before-demo.xml\"[/li]\r\n[li]Add the minimum required xml structure[/li]\r\n[/ol]\r\n\r\nInput\r\n[pre]\r\n$var = \'ABC\';\r\n[/pre]\r\nScript\r\n[pre]\r\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n&lt;modification\r\n                xmlns=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod\"\r\n                xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\r\n                xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vqmod/vqmod/master/vqmod.xsd\">\r\n                >\r\n&lt;id>Before ABC, add 123&lt;/id>\r\n&lt;version>1.0&lt;/version>\r\n&lt;vqmver>2.X&lt;/vqmver>\r\n&lt;author>xxx&lt;/author>\r\n	&lt;file name=\"path/to/myfile.php\">\r\n		&lt;operation info=\"Before ABC, add 123\">\r\n			&lt;search position=\"before\">&lt;![CDATA[\r\n			$var = \'ABC\';\r\n			]]>&lt;/search>\r\n			&lt;add>&lt;![CDATA[\r\n			$var = \'123\';\r\n			]]>&lt;/add>\r\n		&lt;/operation>\r\n	&lt;/file>\r\n&lt;/modification>\r\n[/pre]\r\nOutput\r\n[pre]\r\n$var = \'123\';\r\n$var = \'ABC\';\r\n[/pre]\r\n\"After\" Example\r\n\r\n[ol]\r\n[li]Create a new text file and call it \"after-demo.xml\"[/li]\r\n[li]Add the minimum required xml structure[/li]\r\n[/ol]\r\n\r\nInput\r\n[pre]\r\n$var = \'ABC\';\r\n[/pre]\r\nScript\r\n[pre]\r\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n&lt;modification\r\n                xmlns=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod\"\r\n                xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\r\n                xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vqmod/vqmod/master/vqmod.xsd\">\r\n                >\r\n	&lt;id>After ABC, add 123&lt;/id>\r\n	&lt;version>1.0&lt;/version>\r\n	&lt;vqmver>2.X&lt;/vqmver>\r\n	&lt;author>xxx&lt;/author>\r\n	&lt;file name=\"path/to/myfile.php\">\r\n		&lt;operation info=\"After ABC, add 123\">\r\n			&lt;search position=\"after\">&lt;![CDATA[\r\n			$var = \'ABC\';\r\n			]]>&lt;/search>\r\n			&lt;add>&lt;![CDATA[\r\n			$var = \'123\';\r\n			]]>&lt;/add>\r\n		&lt;/operation>\r\n	&lt;/file>\r\n&lt;/modification>\r\n[/pre]\r\nOutput\r\n[pre]\r\n$var = \'ABC\';\r\n$var = \'123\';\r\n[/pre]\r\n&lt;ignoreif> tag Example (2.3.0+)\r\n\r\n[ol]\r\n[li]Create a new text file and call it \"ignoreif-after-demo.xml\"[/li]\r\n[li]Add the minimum required xml structure[/li]\r\n[/ol]\r\n\r\nInput\r\n[pre]\r\n$var = \'ABC\';\r\n$var2 = \'XYZ\';\r\n[/pre]\r\nScript\r\n[pre]\r\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n&lt;modification\r\n                xmlns=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod\"\r\n                xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\r\n                xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vqmod/vqmod/master/vqmod.xsd\">\r\n                >\r\n	&lt;id>After ABC, add 123 only if XYZ not in file&lt;/id>\r\n	&lt;version>1.0&lt;/version>\r\n	&lt;vqmver>2.X&lt;/vqmver>\r\n	&lt;author>xxx&lt;/author>\r\n	&lt;file name=\"path/to/myfile.php\">\r\n		&lt;operation info=\"After ABC, add 123 if XYZ not in file\">\r\n			&lt;ignoreif>&lt;![CDATA[\r\n			XYZ\r\n			]]>&lt;/ignoreif>\r\n			&lt;search position=\"after\">&lt;![CDATA[\r\n			$var = \'ABC\';\r\n			]]>&lt;/search>\r\n			&lt;add>&lt;![CDATA[\r\n			$var = \'123\';\r\n			]]>&lt;/add>\r\n		&lt;/operation>\r\n	&lt;/file>\r\n&lt;/modification>\r\n[/pre]\r\nOutput\r\n[pre]\r\n$var = \'ABC\';\r\n$var2 = \'XYZ\';\r\n[/pre]\r\n##Multiple files and a base path example (2.3.0+)\r\n\r\nSometimes you require adding the same modification to a number of files at once. Rather than having to do this for individual files and duplicating code for each, you can specify multiple files at once delimited by commas. You can also specify a base path to be used if the files are in a common directory. For example, suppose you want to replace ABC with 123 in the following files\r\n\r\n[ul]\r\n[li]/path/to/a.php[/li]\r\n[li]/path/to/b.php[/li]\r\n[li]/path/to/c.php[/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n\r\n[ol]\r\n[li]Create a new text file and call it \"multi-file-demo.xml\"[/li]\r\n[li]Add the minimum required xml structure[/li]\r\n[/ol]\r\n\r\nInput (all files)\r\n[pre]\r\n$var = \'ABC\';\r\n[/pre]\r\nScript\r\n[pre]\r\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n&lt;modification\r\n                xmlns=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod\"\r\n                xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\r\n                xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vqmod/vqmod/master/vqmod.xsd\">\r\n                >\r\n	&lt;id>Replace ABC with 123&lt;/id>\r\n	&lt;version>1.0&lt;/version>\r\n	&lt;vqmver>2.X&lt;/vqmver>\r\n	&lt;author>xxx&lt;/author>\r\n	&lt;file path=\"path/to/\" name=\"a.php,b.php,c.php\">\r\n		&lt;operation info=\"Replace ABC with 123\">\r\n			&lt;search position=\"replace\">&lt;![CDATA[\r\n			ABC\r\n			]]>&lt;/search>\r\n			&lt;add>&lt;![CDATA[\r\n			123\r\n			]]>&lt;/add>\r\n		&lt;/operation>\r\n	&lt;/file>\r\n&lt;/modification>\r\n[/pre]\r\nOutput (all files)\r\n[pre]\r\n$var = \'123\';\r\n[/pre]\r\n##\'Multi-line Replace\' Example\r\n\r\nvQmod is limited to a single-line search, but you can use the \"offset\" attribute to blindly blanket additional lines of code in the replace.\r\n\r\n[ol]\r\n[li]Create a new text file and call it \"multi-replace-demo.xml\"[/li]\r\n[li]Add the minimum required xml structure[/li]\r\n[/ol]\r\n\r\n    To replace multiple lines we use the \"offset\" attribute with replace. Count the number of total lines to replace and subtract one as the main line is already covered by the replace command. In this example, there are 8 lines of code, so offset would be 7. When possible it\'s advised to avoid doing this\r\n\r\nInput\r\n[pre]\r\npublic function index() {\r\n	$a = rand();\r\n	$b = rand();\r\n	if ($a == $b) {\r\n	echo \'oh noes\';\r\n	return false;\r\n	}\r\n}\r\n[/pre]\r\nScript\r\n[pre]\r\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n&lt;modification\r\n                xmlns=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod\"\r\n                xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\r\n                xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://github.com/vqmod/vqmod https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vqmod/vqmod/master/vqmod.xsd\">\r\n                >\r\n	&lt;id>Replace many lines with one&lt;/id>\r\n	&lt;version>1.0&lt;/version>\r\n	&lt;vqmver>2.X&lt;/vqmver>\r\n	&lt;author>xxx&lt;/author>\r\n	&lt;file name=\"path/to/myfile.php\">\r\n		&lt;operation info=\"Replace index function\">\r\n			&lt;search position=\"replace\" offset=\"7\">&lt;![CDATA[\r\n			public function index() {\r\n			]]>&lt;/search>\r\n			&lt;add>&lt;![CDATA[\r\n			public function index($arr = array()) {\r\n			foreach ($arr as $a) {\r\n			echo $a;\r\n				 }\r\n			}\r\n			]]>&lt;/add>\r\n		&lt;/operation>\r\n	&lt;/file>\r\n&lt;/modification>\r\n[/pre]\r\nOutput\r\n[pre]\r\npublic function index($arr = array()) {\r\nforeach ($arr as $a) {\r\necho $a;\r\n     }\r\n}\r\n[/pre]\r\nNote there are still 7 blank lines. The offset clears the extra 7 lines of code from the input, but the replaced code is added in place of the initial line. So there will be 7 extra spaces after the new code, but it will not affect the code functionality, only the look of the vqcache file which is of no importance.'),
(3, 1, NULL, 'Membuat modal dengan adminLte', NULL, 'Membuat-modal-dengan-adminLte', '', 1, '2020-10-28 01:00:06', '2021-08-04 05:15:57', NULL, '<p>Modal salah satu metode untuk menampilkan data atau apapun dengan cara pop-up, modal ini cukup favorit karena tidak perlu load page dan bisa dikombinasikan dengan ajax supaya tmpilannya bisa diatur sesuai keinginan kita. [br/] #Komponen modal [ul] [li]Cukup download adminLte karena sudah lengkap, html, css dan javascript/jquery[/li] [/ul] #HTML [br/]##Button [pre] &lt;!-- versi codeigniter --&gt; $link = form_button(array( &#39;type&#39; =&gt; &#39;button&#39;, &#39;content&#39; =&gt; &#39;&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-eye&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#39;, &#39;class&#39; =&gt; &#39;btn btn-warning&#39;, &#39;data-toggle&#39; =&gt; &#39;modal&#39;, &#39;data-target&#39; =&gt; &#39;#modal-default&#39; )); **bisa jika mengaktifkan helper html** &lt;!-- /versi codeigniter --&gt; &lt;!-- versi html --&gt; &lt;button type=&quot;button&quot; class=&quot;btn btn-default&quot; data-toggle=&quot;modal&quot; data-target=&quot;#modal-default&quot;&gt; Launch Default Modal &lt;/button&gt; &lt;!-- /versi html --&gt; [/pre] kunci untuk memanggil modal ada pada attribute [strong]data-toggle=&quot;modal&quot; data-target=&quot;#modal-default&quot;[/strong] karena &quot;data-target&quot; akan memanggil [strong]id=&quot;modal-default&quot;[/strong] [br/]##Modal [pre] &lt;div class=&quot;modal fade&quot; id=&quot;modal-default&quot;&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;modal-dialog&quot;&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;modal-content&quot;&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;modal-header&quot;&gt; &lt;button type=&quot;button&quot; class=&quot;close&quot; data-dismiss=&quot;modal&quot; aria-label=&quot;Close&quot;&gt; &lt;span aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&times;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/button&gt; &lt;h4 class=&quot;modal-title&quot;&gt;Default Modal&lt;/h4&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;modal-body&quot;&gt; &lt;p&gt;One fine body&hellip;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;modal-footer&quot;&gt; &lt;button type=&quot;button&quot; class=&quot;btn btn-default pull-left&quot; data-dismiss=&quot;modal&quot;&gt;Close&lt;/button&gt; &lt;button type=&quot;button&quot; class=&quot;btn btn-primary&quot;&gt;Save changes&lt;/button&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;!-- /.modal-content --&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;!-- /.modal-dialog --&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;!-- /.modal --&gt; [/pre] Dengan begini saja seharusnya sudah jalan, tapi kalau begini saja maka cukup sebagai tampilan sederhana saja tidak bisa berubah-ubah makanya agar bisa lebih dinamis digabungkan dengan [strong]ajax[/strong] namun diberi imbuhan sedikit yaitu [strong]ID[/strong] pada body modal [br/]##Modal dengan ajax [pre] &lt;div class=&quot;modal fade&quot; id=&quot;modal-default&quot;&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;modal-dialog&quot;&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;modal-content&quot;&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;modal-header&quot;&gt; &lt;button type=&quot;button&quot; class=&quot;close&quot; data-dismiss=&quot;modal&quot; aria-label=&quot;Close&quot;&gt; &lt;span aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&times;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/button&gt; &lt;h4 class=&quot;modal-title&quot;&gt;Isi Whatsapp&lt;/h4&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;!-- disini kami tambahkan id=&quot;body-modal-data&quot; --&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;modal-body&quot; id=&quot;body-modal-data&quot;&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;modal-footer&quot;&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;!-- /.modal-content --&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;!-- /.modal-dialog --&gt; &lt;/div&gt; [/pre] fungsi dari [strong]id=&quot;body-modal-data&quot;[/strong] adalah tempat dari hasil ajax.[br/] karena akan ditambahi [em]ajax[/em] maka di tombol-nya ditambahi fungsi pada [strong]onClick[/strong]-nya [pre] &lt;!-- versi codeigniter --&gt; $link = form_button(array( &#39;type&#39; =&gt; &#39;button&#39;, &#39;content&#39; =&gt; &#39;&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-eye&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#39;, &#39;class&#39; =&gt; &#39;btn btn-warning&#39;, &#39;data-toggle&#39; =&gt; &#39;modal&#39;, &#39;data-target&#39; =&gt; &#39;#modal-default&#39;, &lt;!-- disini kami tempatkan fungsi yang dimaksud --&gt; &#39;onClick&#39; =&gt; &quot;getData(&#39;$value-&gt;id&#39;,&#39;$value-&gt;id&#39;,&#39;1&#39;)&quot; )); **bisa jika mengaktifkan helper html** &lt;!-- /versi codeigniter --&gt; &lt;!-- versi html --&gt; &lt;!-- disini kami tempatkan diujung script --&gt; &lt;button type=&quot;button&quot; class=&quot;btn btn-default&quot; data-toggle=&quot;modal&quot; data-target=&quot;#modal-default&quot; onClick=&quot;getData(&#39;&lt;?php echo $value-&gt;id; ?&gt;&#39;)&quot;&gt; Launch Default Modal &lt;/button&gt; &lt;!-- /versi html --&gt; [/pre] dimana fungsi tersebut akan memanggil script dari [em]javascript/jquery[/em] [pre] &lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt; function getData(id, id_donatur, don){ var dt = {id:id,id_donatur:id_donatur,don:don} $.post(&quot;&lt;?php echo site_url(&#39;marketing/ajax_get_data&#39;); ?&gt;&quot;, dt,function(data, status){ $(&#39;#body-modal-data&#39;).html(data); }); } &lt;/script&gt; [/pre] ini akan menjalankan program [strong]PHP[/strong] dalam javascript yang disebut [em]ajax[/em] yang akan kami jelaskan pada tulisan yang lain itu saja dulu terima kasih</p>\r\n'),
(4, 1, NULL, 'wordwrap', NULL, 'wordwrap', '', 1, '2020-11-02 12:58:09', '2021-08-03 08:37:08', NULL, '<p>Fungsi wordwrap () membungkus string menjadi baris baru ketika mencapai panjang tertentu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[strong]Catatan:[/strong] Fungsi ini mungkin meninggalkan ruang putih di awal baris.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[strong]Syntax[/strong] [br/] [pre]wordwrap(string,width,break,cut)[/pre]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[pre] &lt;?php $str = &quot;An example of a long word is: Supercalifragulistic&quot;;\r\necho wordwrap($str,15,&quot;&lt;br/&gt;\\n&quot;,TRUE); ?&gt; [/pre]</p>\r\n'),
(5, 1, NULL, 'str_split', NULL, 'str_split', '', 1, '2020-11-03 01:05:41', '2021-07-27 11:05:01', NULL, '[pre]\r\n	&lt;?php\r\n	print_r(str_split(\"Hello\"));\r\n	?>\r\n[/pre]\r\n<span class=\"label label-success\">Hasil</span>\r\n<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"[base_url]imgss/str_split_1-php.png\" />\r\n<hr/>\r\n<strong>Definisi</strong>\r\nFungsi str_split () membagi string menjadi array\r\n[br/][em-merah]The str_split() function splits a string into an array[/em]\r\n[br/][strong]Syntax[/strong]\r\n[pre]\r\n	str_split(string,length)\r\n[/pre]\r\n<hr/>\r\n[pre]\r\n	&lt;?php\r\n		print_r(str_split(\"Hello\",3));\r\n	?>\r\n[/pre]\r\n<span class=\"label label-success\">Hasil</span>\r\n<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"[base_url]imgss/str_split_2-php.png\" />'),
(6, 1, NULL, 'Membuat ajax pada CI dgn method ($.post)', NULL, 'Membuat-ajax-pada-CI-dgn-method-post', '', 1, '2020-11-05 01:30:06', '2020-11-05 02:24:32', NULL, '<p>Buat tombol yang berfungsi untuk membuat aksi [em]javaScript[/em]</p>\r\n[pre]\r\n&lt;!-- versi HTML -->\r\n&lt;a class=\"btn btn-warning btn-flat btn-xs\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#modal-default\" onClick=\"getData(\'&lt;?php echo $value->id; ?>\',\'&lt;?php echo $dtedit->id; ?>\')\">Edit&lt;/a>\r\n\r\n&lt;!-- versi fungsi CI -->\r\n$link = form_button(array(\r\n						\'type\'          => \'button\',\r\n						\'content\'       => \'&lt;i class=\"fa fa-whatsapp\">&lt;/i> Isi\',\r\n						\'class\'			=> \'btn btn-block btn-social btn-success\',\r\n						\'data-toggle\' 	=> \'modal\',\r\n						\'data-target\'	=> \'#modal-default\',\r\n						\'onClick\'		=> \"getData(\'$value->id\',\'$dtedit->id\',\'0\')\"\r\n					));\r\n[/pre]\r\n<p>\r\nKebetulan tombol yang menjadi contoh diatas langsung memanggil fungsi, sebetulnya juga bisa memanfaatka <strong>ID</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nlalu buat fungsi dalam [em]JQuery[/em]\r\n</p>\r\n[pre]\r\n&lt;script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n	function getData(id,id_latihan){\r\n		var dt = {id:id,id_latihan:id_latihan}\r\n		$(\'#body-modal-data\').html(\'...\');\r\n		$.post(\"&lt;?php echo site_url(\'latihan/ajax_get_data\'); ?>\", dt,function(data, status){\r\n			$(\'#body-modal-data\').html(data);\r\n		});\r\n	}\r\n&lt;/script>\r\n[/pre]\r\n<p>\r\nlanjut buat fungsi yang di panggil fungsi ajax diatas\r\n</p>\r\n[pre]\r\npublic function ajax_get_data(){\r\n		$id=$this->input->post(\'id\');\r\n		$id_latihan=$this->input->post(\'id_latihan\');\r\n		$dt=array(\r\n			\'ac\'=>\'edit_riwayat_latihan\',\r\n			\'id\'=>$id,\r\n			\'id_latihan\'=>$id_latihan,\r\n			\'dtriwayat_latihan\'=>$this->M_general->getEdit(\'riwayat_latihan\',$id)\r\n		);\r\n		echo view_one(\'latihan/ajax.php\',$dt);\r\n	}\r\n[/pre]\r\n<p>\r\nlanjut pada [strong]view[/strong]-nya\r\n</p>\r\n[pre]\r\n&lt;?php if($ac==\'edit_riwayat_latihan\'): ?>\r\n	&lt;?php\r\n							$hidden=array(\r\n								\'table\'=>\'riwayat_latihan\',\r\n								\'ac\'=>\'edit\',\r\n								\'id_latihan\'=>$id_latihan\r\n							);\r\n							echo form_open(\'latihan/simpan\',\'class=\"form-horizontal\"\',$hidden); ?>\r\n							&lt;div class=\"form-group\">\r\n								&lt;?php echo form_label(\'Title\', \'title\',array(\'class\'=>\'col-sm-2 control-label\')); ?>\r\n								&lt;div class=\"col-sm-10\">\r\n									&lt;?php\r\n									echo form_input(array(\r\n										\'type\'=>\'text\',\r\n										\'name\'=>\'title\',\r\n								\'value\'=>$dtedit->title,\r\n										\'class\'=>\'form-control\',\r\n										\'id\'=>\'title\',\r\n										\'placeholder\'=>\'Title\'\r\n										)\r\n									);\r\n									?>\r\n								&lt;/div>\r\n							&lt;/div>\r\n							&lt;div class=\"form-group\">\r\n								&lt;?php echo form_label(\'Description\', \'description\',array(\'class\'=>\'col-sm-2 control-label\')); ?>\r\n								&lt;div class=\"col-sm-10\">\r\n									&lt;?php echo form_textarea(array(\r\n										\'name\'=>\'description\',\r\n										\'class\'=>\'form-control\',\r\n							\'id\'=>\'description\',\r\n							\'value\'=>$dtedit->description,\r\n										\'placeholder\'=>\'Description\'\r\n										)\r\n									);\r\n									?>\r\n								&lt;/div>\r\n							&lt;/div>\r\n							&lt;div class=\"form-group\">\r\n								&lt;div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\r\n									&lt;?php echo form_submit(\'save\', \'Submit\',\'class=\"btn btn-danger\"\'); ?>\r\n								&lt;/div>\r\n							&lt;/div>\r\n							&lt;?php echo form_close(); ?>\r\n&lt;?php endif; ?>\r\n[/pre]'),
(7, 1, NULL, 'Cara Membuat Grafik dengan ChartJs', NULL, 'Cara-Membuat-Grafik-dengan-ChartJs', '', 1, '2020-11-11 09:32:54', '2020-11-11 10:51:11', NULL, '<h1>Cara Membuat Grafik dengan ChartJs</h1>\r\n		<p><strong>Membuat Grafik Dengan ChartJs</strong>Grafik merupakan sebuah unsur atau fitur yang paling menambah nilai jual saat aplkasi dengan adanya fitur yang menampilkan data dalam bentuk grafik sangat membantu pengguna dalam membaca jumlah persentase sebuah kumpulan data\r\n		</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>Banyak keuntungan dalam menggunakan grafik. termasuk dapat membuat aplikasi yang kita buat menjadi lebih terlihat profesional. karena data yang awalnya hanya berupa angka bisa terlihat visual. apalagi dengan adanya animasi dan efek yang keren yang membuat tampilan grafik lebih terlihat menarik</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>Namun yang pasti menjadi pertanyaan bagi teman-teman adalah, sulitkah membuat grafik?</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>Jawabaannya tidak, karena sekarang sudah ada banyak plugin javascript yang dapat membantu kita dalam membuat sebuah grafik, apalagi masing-masing plugin grafik mempunyai kelebihan dan kekurangan masing-masing</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>Cara membuat grafik pada aplikasi atau website sngatlah mudah. teman-teman berada pada artikel yang tepat. karena pada tutorial malasngoding.com kali iini kita akan belajar <strong>cara membuat grafik dengan chart.js</strong></p>\r\n		\r\n		<h1>Cara Membuat Grafik dengan ChartJs</h1>\r\n		<p>Teman-teman yang baru mendengar chart.js pasti bingung apa sih chart.js itu silahkan teman-teman simak penjelasan berikut tentang pengertan dan bagaimana cara membuat grafik dengan chart.js dengan mudah dan gratis tentunya.</p>\r\n		<p><a href=\"www.chartjs.org\"><strong>Chart.js</strong></a> adalah salah satu plugin javascript yang dibuat untuk memudahkan atau membantu kita dalam membuat grafik dengan sangat mudah dan cepat. ada banyak sekali pilihan jenis grafik yang bisa kita buat dengan chart.js. diantaranya adalah grafik bari, line, pie, dan banyak deh pokoknya.</p>\r\n		<p>Teman-teman bisa langsung melihaat demo dari jenis-jenis atau model grafik yang bisa kita buat dengan chart.js di website si chart.js ini yaitu di:<a href=\"http://www.chartjs.org/samples/latest/\">http://www.chartjs.org/samples/latest/</a>\r\n		<br/>\r\n		<img src=\"http://localhost/me/dropbox/bahroni_blog/imgss/membuat-grafik-dengan-chartjs.png\" class=\"img-responsive\"/></p>\r\n		<p>Oke langsung saja ya kita mulai tentang cara membuat grafik dengan chart.js</p>\r\n		<h1>Cara Membuat Grafik dengan ChartJs</h1>\r\n		<p>Pada tutorial ini kita akan membuat beberapa jenis contoh grafik dengan menggunakan chart.js</p>\r\n		<p>Langsung saja teman-teman download dulu chart.js nya di <a href=\"https://github.com/chartjs/Chart.js/releases/tag/v2.7.2\">https://github.com/chartjs/Chart.js/releases/tag/v2.7.2</a>. pada saat tutorial ini dibuat, chartjs sudah sampai pada versi terbarunya yaitu v2.7.2</p>\r\n		<p>saya memdownload yang chart.js nya saja. karena saya rasa kita belum membutuhkan package yang lainnya dulu</p>\r\n		<p><img src=\"http://localhost/me/dropbox/bahroni_blog/imgss/cara-membuat-grafik-dengan-chartjs.png\" class=\"img-responsive\"/><span class=\"text-center\">Cara Membuat Grafik Chrt.js</span></p>\r\n		<p>\r\n		Setelah di downlod, extract dan rename nama foldernya menjadi <strong>chartjs</strong>. untuk apa kita rename? supaya lebih mudah kita hubungkan pada project kita. jadi gak perlu menulis sampai versi-versinya seperti v2.7.2 dan bla bla bla. <i class=\"fa fa-smile-o\"></i>\r\n		</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>\r\n		oh ya karena pada contohnya ini saya hanya menggunakan HTML saja dan tidak menggunakan PHP. silahkan teman-teman sesuaikan dengan kebutuhan masing-masing ja. karena saya hanya menggunakan <a href=\"#\">HTML</a>,  maka project nya saya buat di desktop saja projectnya saya buat dalam folder \"grafik\". nanti teman-teman bisa mendownloadnya, link downloadnya sudah saya sertakan di bawah tutorial ini.\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p><img src=\"http://localhost/me/dropbox/bahroni_blog/imgss/cara-install-chartjs-pada-html-atau-php.gif\" class=\"img-responsive\"/><span class=\"text-center\">cara install chhartjs pada html atau php</span></p>\r\n		<p>Selanjutnya buat sebuah file baru dengan nama <strong>index.html</strong> dalam foler grafik.</p>\r\n		<p>Pada file index.html ini saya akan <strong>Membuat sebuah contoh grafik</strong> menggunakan <strong>chart.js</strong></p>\r\n		<p>\r\n		<strong>index.html</strong>\r\n		[pre]\r\n		&lt;!DOCTYPE html>\r\n		&lt;html>\r\n		&lt;head>\r\n			&lt;title>Membuat Grafik Dengan Menggunakan Chart.js - www.malasngoding.com&lt;/title>\r\n			&lt;script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"chartjs/Chart.js\">&lt;/script>\r\n		&lt;/head>\r\n		&lt;body>\r\n			&lt;style type=\"text/css\">\r\n				body{\r\n					font-family: roboto;\r\n				}\r\n			&lt;/style>\r\n		 \r\n			&lt;h2>Tutorial Membuat Grafik Dengan Chart.js - www.malasngoding.com&lt;/h2>\r\n		 \r\n		 \r\n		 \r\n			&lt;div style=\"width: 500px;height: 500px\">\r\n				&lt;canvas id=\"myChart\">&lt;/canvas>\r\n			&lt;/div>\r\n		 \r\n		 \r\n			&lt;script>\r\n				var ctx = document.getElementById(\"myChart\").getContext(\'2d\');\r\n				var myChart = new Chart(ctx, {\r\n					type: \'bar\',\r\n					data: {\r\n						labels: [\"Red\", \"Blue\", \"Yellow\", \"Green\", \"Purple\", \"Orange\"],\r\n						datasets: [{\r\n							label: \'# of Votes\',\r\n							data: [12, 19, 3, 23, 2, 3],\r\n							backgroundColor: [\r\n							\'rgba(255, 99, 132, 0.2)\',\r\n							\'rgba(54, 162, 235, 0.2)\',\r\n							\'rgba(255, 206, 86, 0.2)\',\r\n							\'rgba(75, 192, 192, 0.2)\',\r\n							\'rgba(153, 102, 255, 0.2)\',\r\n							\'rgba(255, 159, 64, 0.2)\'\r\n							],\r\n							borderColor: [\r\n							\'rgba(255,99,132,1)\',\r\n							\'rgba(54, 162, 235, 1)\',\r\n							\'rgba(255, 206, 86, 1)\',\r\n							\'rgba(75, 192, 192, 1)\',\r\n							\'rgba(153, 102, 255, 1)\',\r\n							\'rgba(255, 159, 64, 1)\'\r\n							],\r\n							borderWidth: 1\r\n						}]\r\n					},\r\n					options: {\r\n						scales: {\r\n							yAxes: [{\r\n								ticks: {\r\n									beginAtZero:true\r\n								}\r\n							}]\r\n						}\r\n					}\r\n				});\r\n			&lt;/script>\r\n		&lt;/body>\r\n		&lt;/html>\r\n		[/pre]\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>Akan saya jelaskan dulu sedikit tentang syntx membuat grafik di atas</p>\r\n		<p>Pertama kita hubungkan dulu dengan file Chart.js yang sudah kita download tadi.</p>\r\n		[pre]&lt;script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"chartjs/Chart.js\"></script>[/pre]\r\n		<p>Selanjutnya kita buat sebuah element <canvas>...</canvas> dan kita beri id dengan terserah kita. di sini saya memberi nama id nya dengan \"myChart\".</p>\r\n		[pre]\r\n		&lt;div style=\"width: 500px;height: 500px\">\r\n			&lt;canvas id=\"myChart\">&lt;/canvas>\r\n		&lt;/div>\r\n		[/pre]\r\n		<p>\r\n		kemudian terakhir pada bagian deklarasi chart.js nya kita perintahkan untuk membuat grafik \"2d\" pada id \"myChart\".\r\n		[pre]\r\n		var ctx = document.getElementById(\"myChart\").getContext(\'2d\');\r\n		[/pre]\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n		dengan detail sebagai berikut.\r\n		[pre]\r\n		var myChart = new Chart(ctx, {\r\n			type: \'bar\',\r\n			data: {\r\n				labels: [\"Red\", \"Blue\", \"Yellow\", \"Green\", \"Purple\", \"Orange\"],\r\n				datasets: [{\r\n					label: \'# of Votes\',\r\n					data: [12, 19, 3, 23, 2, 3],\r\n					backgroundColor: [\r\n					\'rgba(255, 99, 132, 0.2)\',\r\n					\'rgba(54, 162, 235, 0.2)\',\r\n					\'rgba(255, 206, 86, 0.2)\',\r\n					\'rgba(75, 192, 192, 0.2)\',\r\n					\'rgba(153, 102, 255, 0.2)\',\r\n					\'rgba(255, 159, 64, 0.2)\'\r\n					],\r\n					borderColor: [\r\n					\'rgba(255,99,132,1)\',\r\n					\'rgba(54, 162, 235, 1)\',\r\n					\'rgba(255, 206, 86, 1)\',\r\n					\'rgba(75, 192, 192, 1)\',\r\n					\'rgba(153, 102, 255, 1)\',\r\n					\'rgba(255, 159, 64, 1)\'\r\n					],\r\n				borderWidth: 1\r\n				}]\r\n			},\r\n			options: {\r\n				scales: {\r\n					yAxes: [{\r\n						ticks: {\r\n							beginAtZero:true\r\n						}\r\n					}]\r\n				}\r\n			}\r\n		});\r\n		[/pre]\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n		kita menetapkan jenis type grafik yang akan kita buat adalah jenis grafik \"bar\"\r\n		[pre]\r\n		type: \'bar\',\r\n		[/pre]\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n		dan untuk data grafik nya dan pengaturan warna yang teman-teman inginkan bisa di atur juga pada [em]datasets[/em] berikut.\r\n		[pre]\r\n		datasets: [{\r\n			label: \'# of Votes\',\r\n			data: [12, 19, 3, 23, 2, 3],\r\n			backgroundColor: [\r\n			\'rgba(255, 99, 132, 0.2)\',\r\n			\'rgba(54, 162, 235, 0.2)\',\r\n			\'rgba(255, 206, 86, 0.2)\',\r\n			\'rgba(75, 192, 192, 0.2)\',\r\n			\'rgba(153, 102, 255, 0.2)\',\r\n			\'rgba(255, 159, 64, 0.2)\'\r\n			],\r\n			borderColor: [\r\n			\'rgba(255,99,132,1)\',\r\n			\'rgba(54, 162, 235, 1)\',\r\n			\'rgba(255, 206, 86, 1)\',\r\n			\'rgba(75, 192, 192, 1)\',\r\n			\'rgba(153, 102, 255, 1)\',\r\n			\'rgba(255, 159, 64, 1)\'\r\n			],\r\n		borderWidth: 1\r\n		}]\r\n		[/pre]\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n		Penasaran dengan hasilnya? mari kita jalankan file index.html yang sudah kita buat di atas.\r\n		<img src=\"http://localhost/me/dropbox/bahroni_blog/imgss/membuat-grafik-dengan-mudah-pada-html-atau-php-1024x544.png\" class=\"img-responsive\"/>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n		Hasilnya keren kan\r\n		</p>'),
(8, 1, NULL, 'Membuat accordion AdminLte', NULL, 'Membuat-accordion-AdminLte', '', 1, '2020-11-11 12:37:00', '2020-11-12 01:09:56', NULL, '<h3>Cara membuat accordion AdminLte</h3>\r\n<p>[pre]\r\n&lt;div class=\"box-group\" id=\"accordion\">\r\n	&lt;!-- we are adding the .panel class so bootstrap.js collapse plugin detects it -->\r\n	&lt;div class=\"panel box box-primary\">\r\n	  &lt;div class=\"box-header with-border\">\r\n		&lt;h4 class=\"box-title\">\r\n		  &lt;a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" href=\"#collapseOne\">\r\n			Collapsible Group Item #1\r\n		  &lt;/a>\r\n		&lt;/h4>\r\n	  &lt;/div>\r\n	  &lt;div id=\"collapseOne\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n		&lt;div class=\"box-body\">\r\n			isi satu\r\n		&lt;/div>\r\n	  &lt;/div>\r\n	&lt;/div>\r\n	&lt;div class=\"panel box box-danger\">\r\n	  &lt;div class=\"box-header with-border\">\r\n		&lt;h4 class=\"box-title\">\r\n		  &lt;a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" href=\"#collapseTwo\">\r\n			Collapsible Group Danger\r\n		  &lt;/a>\r\n		&lt;/h4>\r\n	  &lt;/div>\r\n	  &lt;div id=\"collapseTwo\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\">\r\n		&lt;div class=\"box-body\">\r\n		  isi dua\r\n		&lt;/div>\r\n	  &lt;/div>\r\n	&lt;/div>\r\n	&lt;div class=\"panel box box-success\">\r\n	  &lt;div class=\"box-header with-border\">\r\n		&lt;h4 class=\"box-title\">\r\n		  &lt;a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" href=\"#collapseThree\">\r\n			Collapsible Group Success\r\n		  &lt;/a>\r\n		&lt;/h4>\r\n	  &lt;/div>\r\n	  &lt;div id=\"collapseThree\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\">\r\n		&lt;div class=\"box-body\">\r\n		  isi tiga\r\n		&lt;/div>\r\n	  &lt;/div>\r\n	&lt;/div>\r\n&lt;/div>\r\n[/pre]</p>'),
