(43, 14, 'Keistimewaan memuliakan anak yatim', '<p>sumber <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CS9NQeRFJPY/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CS9NQeRFJPY/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>*Menyantuni Anak Yatim InsyaALLAH dekat dengan Rasulullah Shallallahu &lsquo;Alaihi wa Sallam*</p>\r\n\r\n<p>**Siapa yang ingin dekat dengan rasul? Semua umat muslim pasti ingin dekat dengan Rasulullah Shallallahu &lsquo;Alaihi wa Sallam*. Menyantuni anak yatim adalah hal yang sangat mulia hingga islam menjanjikan balasan yang istimewa dekat dengan Rasul di surga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;*Aku dan orang yang mengasuh atau memelihara anak yatim akan berada di surga begini,&rdquo;lalu beliau mengisyaratkan dengan jari telunjuk dan jari tengah serta mengangkat sedikit.*&rdquo;<br />\r\n(HR. Bukhari, Tirmidzi, Abu Daud dan Ahmad dari sahl bin sa&rsquo;d)</p>\r\n', '2021-08-25 02:36:28', '2021-08-25 09:36:28'),
(44, 12, 'Mukadimah', '<p><strong>Bismillah</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>sebenarnya tidak terlalu sulit cuma mencatat suplier-suplier dan barang yang pernah dibeli disana. jadi akan terbentuk semacam history pembelian yang menarik nanti akan ada pengecekan divisi persediaan untuk kualitas barang kalau layak akan dijual sedangkan kalau tidak layak akan di kembalikan atau diretur kembali kepada supliernya.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>sistem yang akan dibuat akan memberikan urutan suplier yang memberikan harga termurah</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suplier</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>nama</li>\r\n	<li>telp</li>\r\n	<li>provinsi</li>\r\n	<li>kab/kota</li>\r\n	<li>alamat</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Barang</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>nama</li>\r\n	<li>satuan</li>\r\n	<li>luas (optional)</li>\r\n	<li>berat (optional)</li>\r\n	<li>tinggi (optional)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>riwayat pembelian</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Suplier</li>\r\n	<li>Barang</li>\r\n	<li>jumlah pembelian</li>\r\n	<li>harga</li>\r\n	<li>tanggal pembelian</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2021-08-24 19:44:15', '2021-08-25 02:46:38'),
(45, 12, 'Kepikiran untuk tampilan suplier', '<p>Semua data suplier ditampilkan dalam bentuk tabel, dimasing-masing suplier akan ada tombol yang nantinya akan masuk halaman history pembelian dari suplier tersebut dan saat berhasil diload maka modal akan muncul untuk tambah history</p>\r\n\r\n<p>history tidak bisa dihapus hanyak bisa diedit</p>\r\n', '2021-08-27 19:06:06', '2021-08-28 02:06:06'),
(46, 11, 'September 2021', '<ol>\r\n	<li>Bensin Rp. 220.000,-</li>\r\n	<li>Smartfren Rp. 100.000,-&radic;</li>\r\n	<li>Im3/Telkomsel Rp. 50.000,-&radic;</li>\r\n	<li>STNK Rp. 50.000,-</li>\r\n	<li>Jatah 1 Bulan Rp. 100.000,- perminggu Rp. 25.000,-</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>M1 1-3</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jatah bensin Rp. 20.000,-&radic;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>jatah mingguan Rp. 25.000,-&radic;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uang di dompet Rp. 30.000,- jadi bensin Rp. 20.000,- dan uang jajan Rp. 10.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>jatah sudah habis untuk minggu ini jadi masuk uang untuk minggu depan Rp. 50.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>usahakan jangan pakai hingga minggu depan</strong></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>M2 1-7</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;jatah uang Rp. 50.000,- sudah habis dipakai hari sabtu, minggu kemarin saat diwedusan jadi tadi senin harus ambil lagi uang Rp. 100.000,- untuk jatah bensin 1 minggu sekaligus jatah jajan minggu ke-2&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Saldo Rp. 100.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jatah bensin Rp. 60.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:500px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Hari</td>\r\n			<td>Penjelasn</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Senin</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>jatah Rp. 20.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>dibelikan bensin Rp. 15.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>dibelikan jajan Faqih Rp. 4.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>[span-merah]Sisa Rp. 1.000,-[/span]</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Rabu</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Jatah Rp. 20.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>dibelikan bensin Rp. 20.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>[span-merah]sisa Rp. 0,- [/span]</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Jum&#39;at</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Jatah Rp. 20.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>dibelikan bensin Rp. 15.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>dibelikan jajan faqih Rp. 4.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>[span-merah]Sisa Rp. 1.000,-[/span]</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\nTotal sisa bensin Rp. 2.000,-<br />\r\n<s><strong>Uang jajan Rp. 40.000,-</strong></s><br />\r\nbeli sate mainan Rp. 2.000,- + beli burung Rp. 5.000,- + beli kurung Rp. 25.000,- &rArr; Rp. 32.000,-<br />\r\njadi sisa uang jajan Rp.40.000,- (-) Rp. 32.000,- = <strong>Rp. 8.000,-</strong></blockquote>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>&nbsp;M3 1-7</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Jatah tinggal Rp. 8.000,-&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Saldo Rp. 60.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jatah bensin Rp. 40.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:500px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Hari</td>\r\n			<td>Penjelasn</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Selasa</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>jatah Rp. 20.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>dibelikan bensin Rp. 20.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>[span-merah]sisa Rp. 0,- [/span]</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Kamis</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Jatah Rp. 20.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>dibelikan Rp. 15.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>[span-merah]sisa Rp. 5.000,- [/span]</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>Total sisa bensin Rp. 0,-<br />\r\n<strong>Uang jajan <s>Rp. 10.000,-</s>, Rp. 12.000,-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><s>beli susu milo Rp. 3.000,-</s> beli sosis sama snack Rp. 2.000,- pompa ban Rp. 2.000,- belikan faqih susu Rp. 3.000,-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>uang awal Rp. 5.000,- ketambahan Rp. 12.000,- plus Rp. 2.000,- untuk uang jajan ketambahan dari hasil beli oli motor Rp. 7.000,-</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n', '2021-08-31 03:24:55', '2021-09-17 03:54:15'),
(47, 15, 'Tahap 1', '<p>Menginstall elementor dan membuat catatan di <a href=\"http://localhost:8888/me/dropbox/bahroni_blog/index.php/latihan/action?ac=riwayat_latihan&amp;id=15\">http://localhost:8888/me/dropbox/bahroni_blog/index.php/latihan/action?ac=riwayat_latihan&amp;id=15</a></p>\r\n', '2021-09-21 20:39:26', '2021-09-22 03:39:26');
INSERT INTO `riwayat_latihan` (`id`, `id_latihan`, `title`, `description`, `createAt`, `updateAt`) VALUES
(48, 11, 'Oktober 2021', '<p><strong>Jatah Rp. 500.000,-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Bensin Rp. 200.000,-</li>\r\n	<li>Smartfren Rp. 100.000,-&radic;</li>\r\n	<li>Im3/Telkomsel Rp. 30.000,-&radic;</li>\r\n	<li>service sepeda Rp. 50.000,-</li>\r\n	<li>Jatah 1 Bulan Rp. 100.000,- perminggu Rp. 25.000,-</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>M1</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n', '2021-10-04 18:34:09', '2021-10-08 04:08:59'),
(49, 16, 'The connection was reset', '<p>The connection was reset</p>\r\n\r\n<p>error macam apa ini</p>\r\n', '2021-10-14 05:26:20', '2021-10-14 12:26:21'),
(50, 16, 'Perubahan IP utama', '<p>http://103.82.241.220/gatesystem/<br />\r\nusername : jfx_2020<br />\r\npassword : jfx2020</p>\r\n', '2021-10-15 02:04:20', '2021-10-15 09:04:20'),
(51, 17, 'Pengembangan kamus', '<p>desain database</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>tabel bahasa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>id, nama</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tabel kata</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>id, id_bahasa, nama, arti, penjelasan</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n', '2021-10-15 02:32:54', '2021-10-15 09:32:54'),
(52, 16, 'OS Server', '<p>Server menggunakan OS <strong>CENTOS</strong></p>\r\n', '2021-10-25 19:08:28', '2021-10-26 02:08:28'),
(53, 7, '<del>Make read file txt for Broadcast each donatur</del>', '<p>ada masalah dalam membuat broadcast yang disimpan pada <em>database</em> yaitu database tidak bisa menyimpan icon-icon yang whatsapp sediakan, sehingga jika dipaksakan maka icon-icon itu akan diubah menjadi <del>?????</del> untuk itu harus dimasukkan daam file .txt lalu diambil melalui library dan ditampilkan di view</p>\r\n\r\n<p>step-step pengerjaan</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>buat tabel untuk menampung text apa saja yang adadone</li>\r\n	<li>setelah buat tabel buat menu dibawah group tema karena hampir mirip nanti tampilannyadone</li>\r\n	<li>buat method atau fungsi di controllerdone</li>\r\n	<li>buat library untuk load file dan uji cobadone</li>\r\n	<li>Jika sudah berhasildone</li>\r\n	<li>buat CURD untuk tabel yang sudah dibuatdone</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '2022-05-30 19:01:09', '2022-06-07 10:55:35'),
(54, 7, 'Membuat absen dengan cara login', '<p>login bisa dijadikan alat untuk absen, jadi awal datang kita login itu awal masuk tidak peduli jam berapa di pagi hari yang pasti kalau terlalu pagi dikasih keterangan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>logout bisa untuk pulang tapi bagaimana jika logout pada sebelum jam pulang maka dianggap logout biasa, logout bisa dianggap pulang kalau posisi logout sesudah ashar.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>bagaimana jika lupa logout maka dianggap tidak pulang hari itu dianggap lupa logout</p>\r\n', '2022-06-07 03:54:55', '2022-06-07 10:54:55'),
(55, 7, '<del>membuat frontend untuk bmh.yarid.id</del>', '<p>tujuannya memantau kinerja marketing online</p>\r\n\r\n<p>yang akan dibuat</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>apa saja yang dikerjakan seharian</li>\r\n	<li>berapa banyak pesan yang dikirim perhari</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Penjelasan</th>\r\n			<th>Status</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Jumlah donatur yang dikirimi pesan</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>jumlah data yang dimasukkan hari itu</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>kegiatan harian</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>setting frontend</td>\r\n			<td>done</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2022-06-07 20:58:19', '2022-06-17 10:15:55'),
(56, 7, '<del>Membuat frontend</del>', '<p>Cara buat table freeze kolom pertama</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[pre]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>/* CSS */</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>.table &gt; thead:first-child &gt; tr:first-child &gt; th:first-child {\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    display: inline-block;\r\n    background-color: red;\r\n    height: 100%;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.table &gt; tbody &gt; tr &gt; td:first-child {\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    display: inline-block;\r\n    background-color: red;\r\n    height: 100%;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.table &gt; thead:first-child &gt; tr:first-child &gt; th:nth-child(2) {\r\n    padding-left: 40px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.table &gt; tbody &gt; tr &gt; td:nth-child(2) {\r\n    padding-left: 50px !important;\r\n}</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>[/pre]</p>\r\n', '2022-06-15 22:42:52', '2022-06-17 10:15:37'),
(57, 7, 'Revisi #1', '<ol>\r\n	<li>karantina 1 donatu &quot;profile donatur&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>mencari donatur berdasarkan nama/nomer di karantina/pasif donatur</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '2022-06-17 03:20:46', '2022-06-17 10:20:46'),
(58, 19, 'Task MAIL', '<p>Search &quot;<a href=\"mailto:customer@obajatour.com\" target=\"_blank\">customer@obajatour.com</a>&quot; (7 hits in 6 files of 23419 searched)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; C:\\xampp\\htdocs\\me\\obaja\\obajatour\\api\\include\\fungsi.php (1 hit)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Line 1591: $mail-&gt;Username = &#39;<a href=\"mailto:customer@obajatour.com\" target=\"_blank\">customer@obajatour.com</a>&#39;;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;// SMTP username</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; C:\\xampp\\htdocs\\me\\obaja\\obajatour\\api\\test_email.php (1 hit)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Line&nbsp; 84: //&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;$mail-&gt;Username = &#39;<a href=\"mailto:customer@obajatour.com\" target=\"_blank\">customer@obajatour.com</a>&#39;;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;// SMTP username</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; C:\\xampp\\htdocs\\me\\obaja\\obajatour\\application\\controllers\\Pages.php (2 hits)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Line 272:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;$mail-&gt;Username = &#39;<a href=\"mailto:customer@obajatour.com\" target=\"_blank\">customer@obajatour.com</a>&#39;;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;// SMTP username</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Line 311:&nbsp; &nbsp;//&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;$config[&#39;smtp_user&#39;] = &#39;<a href=\"mailto:customer@obajatour.com\" target=\"_blank\">customer@obajatour.com</a>&#39;;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; C:\\xampp\\htdocs\\me\\obaja\\obajatour\\application\\controllers\\Tour.php (1 hit)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Line&nbsp; 712:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;$config[&#39;smtp_user&#39;] = &#39;<a href=\"mailto:customer@obajatour.com\" target=\"_blank\">customer@obajatour.com</a>&#39;;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; C:\\xampp\\htdocs\\me\\obaja\\obajatour\\assets\\development\\api\\include\\fungsi.php (1 hit)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Line 1592: $mail-&gt;Username = &#39;<a href=\"mailto:customer@obajatour.com\" target=\"_blank\">customer@obajatour.com</a>&#39;;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;// SMTP username</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; C:\\xampp\\htdocs\\me\\obaja\\obajatour\\assets\\development\\api\\test_email.php (1 hit)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Line&nbsp; 84: //&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;$mail-&gt;Username = &#39;<a href=\"mailto:customer@obajatour.com\" target=\"_blank\">customer@obajatour.com</a>&#39;;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;// SMTP username</p>\r\n', '2022-08-03 18:27:47', '2022-08-04 01:27:47'),
(59, 19, 'Task Email #yangHarusDiBuat', '<p>[02/08, 20:49] Jo!!Client: to: <a href=\"mailto:counter@obajatour.com\" target=\"_blank\">counter@obajatour.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>cc: <a href=\"mailto:budiman@obajatour.com\" target=\"_blank\">budiman@obajatour.com</a>, <a href=\"mailto:joshualeonard888@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">joshualeonard888@gmail.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>[02/08, 20:56] Jo!!Client: judul email:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>New Tour Booking from Website [Nama Paket Tour]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[02/08, 20:57] Jo!!Client: itu yg tour name, bpk ambil dari nama tournya</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[02/08, 20:57] Jo!!Client: name, email, total pax, booking date itu hrsnya bisa bpk dptin jg valuenya</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[02/08, 20:57] Jo!!Client: dari formnya</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[02/08, 20:57] Jo!!Client: isi email:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hi,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There is a new Tour Booking from Website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tour Name:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Name:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phone:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Total Pax:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Booking Date:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please check the Backoffice to see the details.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[02/08, 20:59] Jo!!Client: ini notifnya terkirim saat di sisi frontend, customer ke menu tour --&gt; pilih area --&gt; pilih tour --&gt; pilih tanggal --&gt; klik book now --&gt; isi form --&gt; *submit*</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[02/08, 20:59] Jo!!Client: total pax = num of members</p>\r\n', '2022-08-03 20:07:56', '2022-08-04 03:07:56'),
(60, 19, '{URGENT]Sebelum senin harus sudah selesai', '<p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1PuXGOt6UQ-Ntk_SAUrXOS7gE7sEK32c-ViFmcScrKfs/edit?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">Klik</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>tambah column date of birth pada reservation_tour</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[code]ALTER TABLE `reservation_tour`&nbsp; ADD `dob` DATE NULL DEFAULT NULL&nbsp; AFTER `pay_status`;[/code]</p>\r\n', '2022-08-07 04:25:36', '2022-08-07 12:59:34'),
(61, 19, 'penambahan table', '<p>[pre]<br />\r\ncreate table reservation_tour_members_visa(<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;id_member bigint,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;id_jenis_visa bigint null,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;id_harga_visa bigint null,<br />\r\n)Engine=InnoDB;<br />\r\n[/pre]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[pre]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ALTER TABLE `reservation_tour_members`&nbsp; ADD `pass_img` TEXT NULL&nbsp; AFTER `pass_exp`;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[/pre]</p>\r\n', '2022-08-11 04:22:35', '2022-08-15 01:38:47'),
(62, 19, 'Settingan email smtp', '<p>public function testmail(){<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $config[&#39;protocol&#39;] = &quot;smtp&quot;;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $config[&#39;smtp_host&#39;] = &#39;smtp.gmail.com&#39;;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $config[&#39;smtp_port&#39;] = 587;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $config[&#39;smtp_user&#39;] = &#39;customer@obajatour.com&#39;;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $config[&#39;smtp_pass&#39;] = &#39;Powerobaja&#39;;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $config[&#39;smtp_crypto&#39;] = &#39;tls&#39;;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $config[&#39;mailtype&#39;] = &#39;html&#39;;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $config[&#39;charset&#39;] = &#39;utf-8&#39;;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $config[&#39;wordwrap&#39;] = TRUE;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$this-&gt;email-&gt;initialize($config);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$this-&gt;email-&gt;set_newline(&quot;\\r\\n&quot;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $this-&gt;email-&gt;from(&#39;tour@obajatour.com&#39;, &#39;Obaja Tour&#39;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $this-&gt;email-&gt;to(&#39;praymeid@gmail.com&#39;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $this-&gt;email-&gt;subject(&#39;Obajatour bookingtour travel&#39;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $this-&gt;email-&gt;message(&#39;&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;title&gt;Ktoś wyświetlił stronę!&lt;/title&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ktoś wyświetlił stronę&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;&#39;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; if ($this-&gt;email-&gt;send()) {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; echo &#39;Your Email has successfully been sent.&#39;;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; } else {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; show_error($this-&gt;email-&gt;print_debugger());<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; }<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}</p>\r\n', '2022-08-12 03:26:28', '2022-08-12 10:26:28'),
(63, 20, '13 Agustus 2022', '<p>277 - 318</p>\r\n', '2022-08-12 18:03:17', '2022-08-13 01:03:17'),
(64, 19, 'modifikasi database obajatour', '<p>[pre]ALTER TABLE `tour_main`&nbsp; ADD `fake_num_of_members` INT NOT NULL DEFAULT &#39;0&#39;&nbsp; AFTER `status_deleted`;[/pre]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[pre]<code><a href=\"http://localhost/phpmyadmin/url.php?url=https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/alter-table.html\" target=\"mysql_doc\">ALTER</a> <a href=\"http://localhost/phpmyadmin/url.php?url=https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/alter-table.html\" target=\"mysql_doc\">TABLE</a> `reservation_tour` CHANGE `country` `country` <a href=\"http://localhost/phpmyadmin/url.php?url=https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/string-types.html\" target=\"mysql_doc\">CHAR</a>(10) <a href=\"http://localhost/phpmyadmin/url.php?url=https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/charset.html\" target=\"mysql_doc\">CHARACTER</a> <a href=\"http://localhost/phpmyadmin/url.php?url=https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/charset.html\" target=\"mysql_doc\">SET</a> latin1 <a href=\"http://localhost/phpmyadmin/url.php?url=https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/charset-collations.html\" target=\"mysql_doc\">COLLATE</a> latin1_swedish_ci NULL <a href=\"http://localhost/phpmyadmin/url.php?url=https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/miscellaneous-functions.html#function_default\" target=\"mysql_doc\">DEFAULT</a> &#39;ID&#39;; </code>[/pre]</p>\r\n', '2022-08-15 23:20:55', '2022-08-16 06:27:52'),
(65, 19, 'Cara Buat Validasi HTML5 dengan jQuery', '<p>[pre]<br />\r\nfunction bookerNotBlank(){<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;var elements = $(&quot;.booker&quot;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; for (var i = 0; i &lt; elements.length; i++) {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; elements[i].oninvalid = function(e) {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; e.target.setCustomValidity(&quot;&quot;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; if (!e.target.validity.valid) {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; e.target.setCustomValidity(&quot;This field cannot be left blank&quot;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; }<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; };<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; elements[i].oninput = function(e) {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; e.target.setCustomValidity(&quot;&quot;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; };<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; }<br />\r\n}<br />\r\n[/pre]</p>\r\n', '2022-08-17 03:47:57', '2022-08-17 10:47:57'),
(66, 19, '', '<p>[pre]ALTER TABLE `users`&nbsp; ADD `dob` DATE NULL&nbsp; AFTER `id_city`,&nbsp; ADD `mr_mrs` ENUM(&#39;mr&#39;,&#39;mrs&#39;,&#39;miss&#39;,&#39;mstr&#39;,&#39;inf&#39;,&#39;ms&#39;) NULL&nbsp; AFTER `dob`,&nbsp; ADD `hobbies` text NULL&nbsp; AFTER `mr_mrs`,&nbsp; ADD `pass_num` varchar(100) NULL&nbsp; AFTER `hobbies`,&nbsp; ADD `pass_exp` DATE NULL&nbsp; AFTER `pass_num`,&nbsp; ADD `pass_img` text NULL&nbsp; AFTER `pass_exp`, ADD `pass_issue` text NULL&nbsp; AFTER `pass_img`, ADD `visa_country` bigint NULL&nbsp; AFTER `pass_issue`, ADD `visa_exp` DATE NULL&nbsp; AFTER `visa_country`, ADD `visa_img` TEXT NULL&nbsp; AFTER `visa_country`;[/pre]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[pre]<br />\r\nALTER TABLE `users`&nbsp; ADD `id_country` CHAR(10) NULL&nbsp; AFTER `ReferalShare`,&nbsp; ADD `id_city` CHAR(10) NULL&nbsp; AFTER `id_country`;<br />\r\n[/pre]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[pre]ALTER TABLE `reservation_tour`&nbsp; ADD `userid` BIGINT;[/pre]</p>\r\n', '2022-08-19 00:08:37', '2022-08-21 10:13:17'),
(67, 19, 'checkbox datepicker', '<p>[pre]</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>$(&quot;#txtSearch&quot;).datepicker(&quot;enable&quot;);\r\n$(&quot;#txtSearch&quot;).datepicker(&quot;disable&quot;);</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p><code>[/pre]</code></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This disables the entire textbox. So may be you can use <a href=\"http://jqueryui.com/demos/datepicker/#method-destroy\"><code>datepicker.destroy()</code></a> instead:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[pre]</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>$(document).ready(function() {\r\n    $(&quot;#ddlSearchType&quot;).change(function() {\r\n        if ($(this).val() == &quot;Required Date&quot; || $(this).val() == &quot;Submitted Date&quot;) {\r\n            $(&quot;#txtSearch&quot;).datepicker();\r\n        }\r\n        else {\r\n            $(&quot;#txtSearch&quot;).datepicker(&quot;destroy&quot;);\r\n        }\r\n    }).change();\r\n});</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n[/pre]</p>\r\n', '2022-08-24 23:22:54', '2022-08-25 06:22:54'),
(68, 20, 'tambahan keterangan', '<div dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<div>Projects itu ambil fee 12% ya?</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Kalo nggak mas nya naekin bid nya jadi 600 ribu.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Web nya Closecrowds.com</div>\r\n<div>Contoh product yang udah di buat:</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://www.closecrowds.com/downloads/diverge-ai-robotics-website-themes/\">https://www.closecrowds.com/downloads/diverge-ai-robotics-website-themes/</a></div>\r\n<div>Content nya ambil dari sini</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://elements.envato.com/wordpress/template-kits/sort-by-latest\">https://elements.envato.com/wordpress/template-kits/sort-by-latest</a></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Mas nya butuh download image nya, terus copy deskripsi nya (nggak semua deskripsi tapi hanya sampai batas feature), terus copy link nya.</div>\r\n<div>Kalo theme nya bagus, mas klik feature product nya, kalo theme nya kurang bagus, mas nya turunin harga jadi 15 dollar. Terus input link download yang di ambil dari Mega.nz (di mega ini ada 2400 produk jadi mas gunakan fitur search buat cari sesuai judul)\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Pilih kategori sesuai envato, input tags dan seterusnya yang detil2 gak banyak perubahan.\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Cuma di deskripsi ada keyword misal Template kit elementor, itu orang awam ga paham jadi mas nya edit dikit misal jadi wordpress theme, dan sejenisnya spya orang awam gak bingung.\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Nanti ada link report yang saya minta sesuai format karena dari link itu saya harus buat link live preview.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Sepertinya itu saja, mas nya lihat2 dulu, nanti jam 8 begitu saya test untuk lihat kerjaan mas nya.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Di envato ini ada 2400 produk. \r\n</div>\r\n<div>Saya pekerjakan pekerja lain yang kerja untuk posting 1200, \r\n</div>\r\n<div>dia posting untuk produk ini<div>\r\n<div>Automotive &amp; Transport	76</div>\r\n<div>Blog &amp; Podcast	31</div>\r\n<div>Education	75</div>\r\n<div>Event &amp; Entertainment	64</div>\r\n<div>Fashion &amp; Beauty	102</div>\r\n<div>Finance &amp; Law	109</div>\r\n<div>Fiood &amp; Drink	143</div>\r\n<div>Health &amp; Medical	146</div>\r\n<div>News &amp; Magazine	38</div>\r\n<div>Non Profit &amp; Religion	50</div>\r\n<div>Personal &amp; CV	64</div>\r\n<div>Photography	37</div>\r\n<div>Real Estate &amp; Construction	148</div>\r\n<div>Shopping &amp; Commerce	106</div>\r\n<div>Wedding	22</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Mas nya kerjakan produk selain dari kategori ini.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>', '2022-09-07 04:47:55', '2022-09-07 11:47:55'),
(69, 19, 'backup backend/v_footer.php', '<hr/>\r\nline 337\r\n[pre]\r\n	$(\'#formTourBooking\').on(\'submit\',function(e){\r\n		e.preventDefault()\r\n		let dob=$(\'input[name=\"dob\"]\').val()\r\n		let first_name=$(\'input[name=\"first_name\"]\').val()\r\n		let last_name=$(\'input[name=\"last_name\"]\').val()\r\n		\r\n		const emailValue=[first_name,last_name,dob]\r\n		\r\n		$.post(\'<?php echo site_url(\"ajax/checkEmailValid\"); ?>\',{email:emailValue},function(data){\r\n			let num = parseInt(data)\r\n		\r\n			if(num > 0){\r\n				$(\'input[name=\"first_name\"]\').parent().addClass(\'has-error\')\r\n				$(\'input[name=\"last_name\"]\').parent().addClass(\'has-error\')\r\n				$(\'input[name=\"dob\"]\').parent().addClass(\'has-error\')\r\n\r\n				if($(\'#first_name_alert\').length > 0){\r\n					$(\'#first_name_alert\').text(\'First Name is already exists\')\r\n				}else{\r\n					$(\'input[name=\"first_name\"]\').parent().append(\'<span id=\"first_name_alert\" class=\"first_name_alert text-red\">First Name is already exists</span>\')\r\n				}\r\n				\r\n				if($(\'#last_name_alert\').length > 0){\r\n					$(\'#last_name_alert\').text(\'Last Name is already exists\')\r\n				}else{\r\n					$(\'input[name=\"last_name\"]\').parent().append(\'<span id=\"last_name_alert\" class=\"last_name_alert text-red\">Last Name is already exists</span>\')\r\n				}\r\n				\r\n				if($(\'#dob_alert\').length > 0){\r\n					$(\'#dob_alert\').text(\'Date Of Birth is already exists\')\r\n				}else{\r\n					$(\'input[name=\"dob\"]\').parent().append(\'<span id=\"dob_alert\" class=\"dob_alert text-red\">Date Of Birth is already exists</span>\')\r\n				}\r\n				\r\n			}else{\r\n				$(\'input[name=\"first_name\"]\').parent().removeClass(\'has-error\')\r\n				$(\'#first_name_alert\').text(\'\')\r\n				$(\'input[name=\"last_name\"]\').parent().removeClass(\'has-error\')\r\n				$(\'#last_name_alert\').text(\'\')\r\n				$(\'input[name=\"dob\"]\').parent().removeClass(\'has-error\')\r\n				$(\'#dob_alert\').text(\'\')\r\n			}\r\n		})\r\n		/*let i_plus=$(\'.has-error\').length\r\n		if(i_plus===0) this.submit()*/\r\n	})\r\n[/pre]', '2022-10-01 22:06:32', '2022-10-02 05:06:32'),
(70, 19, 'tips dan trik javascript/jQuery', '<p>1. Buat scrool auto top</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>[code]<code>window.scrollTo({top: 0, behavior: &#39;smooth&#39;});</code>[/code]</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n', '2022-10-01 23:33:02', '2022-10-02 06:35:36'),
(71, 19, 'backup backend/v_footer.php', '[pre]\r\nlet dob=$(\'input[name=\"dob\"]\').val()\r\n		let first_name=$(\'input[name=\"first_name\"]\').val()\r\n		let last_name=$(\'input[name=\"last_name\"]\').val()\r\n		\r\n		const emailValue=[first_name,last_name,dob]\r\n		\r\n		$.post(\'<?php echo site_url(\"ajax/checkEmailValid\"); ?>\',{email:emailValue},function(data){\r\n			let num = parseInt(data)\r\n		\r\n			if(num > 0){\r\n				$(\'#main-alert\').html(\'<i class=\"fa fa-ban\"></i> First Name, Last Name and Date Of birth could potentially already exist\')\r\n				\r\n				window.scrollTo({top: 0, behavior: \'smooth\'})\r\n			}else{\r\n				$(\'#main-alert\').html(\'\')\r\n			}\r\n		})\r\n[/pre]', '2022-10-02 18:32:46', '2022-10-03 01:32:46'),
(72, 20, 'SQ laporan', '<p>[pre]select id,url from laporan_wp where edisi=2 and url&lt;&gt;&#39;&#39; and url_preview&lt;&gt;&#39;OFF&#39;[/pre]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[pre]select count(id) from laporan_wp where edisi=2 and url_preview=&#39;OFF&#39;[/pre]</p>\r\n', '2022-10-04 23:41:30', '2022-10-05 06:53:12'),
